106
00:10:48,266 --> 00:10:54,027
[SPEAKER_00]: So, today we gather here to discuss some of the most pivotal aspects that shape the future of our community.

107
00:10:54,748 --> 00:11:02,950
[SPEAKER_00]: Equity inclusion, quality education, safe learning environments, education equity, supporting staff and educators, and community collaboration.

108
00:11:03,590 --> 00:11:12,872
[SPEAKER_00]: These elements form the basis of a thriving educational ecosystem that nurtures the potential of every individual regardless of their background, abilities, or circumstances.

109
00:11:13,816 --> 00:11:16,397
[SPEAKER_00]: At the heart of my mission is the pursuit of equity inclusion.

110
00:11:16,997 --> 00:11:30,423
[SPEAKER_00]: It is our collective responsibility to ensure that every student, regardless of their abilities, race, gender, socioeconomic status, or any other identifiers, receives an education that not only imparts knowledge, but also instills a sense of belonging.

111
00:11:41,137 --> 00:11:43,538
[SPEAKER_00]: strengths, and challenges deserve tailored attention.

112
00:11:44,318 --> 00:11:47,398
